OL,3,CPotential timeline for an Andy Burnham
OL,4,Cleadership challenge
OL,6,FWritten by ITV News multimedia
OL,7,Fproducer Connor Parker
OL,9,FAndy Burnham has announced he is
OL,10,Fplanning to run in the upcoming by-
OL,11,Felection in Makerfield, making a
OL,12,Fchallenge to Keir Starmer's
OL,13,Fpremiership look even more likely.
OL,15,FBurnham confirmed his intention to run
OL,16,Fafter MP Josh Simmons resigned his
OL,17,Fseat on Thursday, explicitly saying he
OL,18,Fwas doing it so that the Manchester
OL,19,Fmayor could run.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
