OL,3,CPotential timeline for an Andy Burnham
OL,4,Cleadership challenge
OL,6,FBut the road to Number 10 is fraught
OL,7,Fwith risks, and Burnham has a long way
OL,8,Fto go before he could eventually
OL,9,Fchallenge Starmer for the leadership,
OL,10,Flet alone win it.
OL,12,FHere, ITV News looks at what a
OL,13,Fpossible timeframe would look like and
OL,14,Fall the hurdles he will have to pass.
OL,16,FSelected as a candidate in Makerfield
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
