OL,3,CPotential timeline for an Andy Burnham
OL,4,Cleadership challenge
OL,6,FStarmer is not expected to block
OL,7,FBurnham's attempt to run, meaning
OL,8,FLabour's National Executive Council
OL,9,F(NEC) is likely to vote to approve his
OL,10,Fcandidacy this weekend.
OL,12,FSome sources have said it was "not
OL,13,Fclear" that Burnham would get the
OL,14,Fbacking of the NEC, but he has
OL,15,Freceived the backing of some of the
OL,16,Fmajor trade unions that have a vote in
OL,17,Fthe decision.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
