OL,3,CPotential timeline for an Andy Burnham
OL,4,Cleadership challenge
OL,6,FOnce approved by the NEC, Burnham will
OL,7,Fthen need to be selected as the
OL,8,Fcandidate in the seat, although
OL,9,Fpressure from senior members of the
OL,10,FLabour Party on the local branch may
OL,11,Fmake it unlikely another candidate
OL,12,Fwould challenge his selection.
OL,14,FCandidate selection usually takes
OL,15,Faround a week, with Reform saying they
OL,16,Fwere accepting applicants until Sunday.
OL,18,FThe Greens have also said they plan to
OL,19,Frun in the seat.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
