OL,3,CPotential timeline for an Andy Burnham
OL,4,Cleadership challenge
OL,6,FHow long will the Makerfield by-
OL,7,Felection take?
OL,9,FBy-elections usually take place within
OL,10,F4-6 weeks of an MP resigning from
OL,11,Ftheir seat, but it can sometimes be a
OL,12,Ffew months.
OL,14,FIn the Gorton and Denton by-election,
OL,15,FGywnne resigned on January 22, and the
OL,16,Felection was held on February 26.
OL,18,FBy-elections are typically held on
OL,19,FThursdays, placing the most likely
OL,20,Fdates on June 18 or June 25.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
