OL,3,CPotential timeline for an Andy Burnham
OL,4,Cleadership challenge
OL,6,FMakerfield has traditionally been a
OL,7,Fsafe Labour seat, but recently Reform
OL,8,Fhas been making major gains in the
OL,9,Farea.
OL,11,FIn Wigan, where Makerfield is, Labour
OL,12,Flost all 22 of its councillors in last
OL,13,Fweek's local election, with Reform
OL,14,Fpicking up 24 of the 25 seats up for
OL,15,Fgrabs.
OL,17,FIn the eight Makerfield wards that
OL,18,Fvoted in the local election, Reform
OL,19,Fsecured 50% of the vote while Labour
OL,20,Fgot 23%.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
