OL,3,CPotential timeline for an Andy Burnham
OL,4,Cleadership challenge
OL,6,FIf he wins, how long until Burnham can
OL,7,Fchallenge Starmer?
OL,9,FIf Burnham wins, he will be sworn in
OL,10,Fas an MP in the House of Commons the
OL,11,Ffollowing week, when he can then take
OL,12,Fup his seat.
OL,14,FAfter that, it will be up to him and
OL,15,Fhis fellow Labour MPs over when to
OL,16,Ftrigger a leadership challenge. They
OL,17,Fmight not choose to do it on the first
OL,18,Fday Burnham is in Parliament.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
