OL,3,CPotential timeline for an Andy Burnham
OL,4,Cleadership challenge
OL,6,FFor a leadership election to be
OL,7,Ftriggered under Labour Party rules,
OL,8,F20% of the party's MPs (81 MPs
OL,9,Fcurrently) need to back a single
OL,10,Freplacement candidate first.
OL,12,FOnce that is done, the NEC then
OL,13,Farranges a timetable for the election,
OL,14,Fwhich historically has varied
OL,15,Fsignificantly in time length.
OL,17,FThere has never been a direct
OL,18,Fchallenge to the leader of the Labour
OL,19,FParty while they are prime minister.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
