OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1778889776
OL,3,CPotential timeline for an Andy Burnham
OL,4,Cleadership challenge
OL,6,FThe party would likely want the
OL,7,Fcontest to be as short as possible to
OL,8,Freduce the amount of time the
OL,9,Fcountry's leadership was in question.
OL,11,FThe closest comparison is the race to
OL,12,Freplace Boris Johnson when he resigned
OL,13,Fon July 7, 2022.
OL,15,FLiz Truss won the contest on September
OL,16,F5, meaning it took around two months
OL,17,Fto run the contest, but it is worth
OL,18,Fnoting that the Labour Party and the
OL,19,FConservative Party are governed by
OL,20,Fvery different rules.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
