OL,3,CPotential timeline for an Andy Burnham
OL,4,Cleadership challenge
OL,6,FSeveral Labour MPs who have called for
OL,7,FStarmer to stand aside have urged him
OL,8,Fto set out a timetable for his orderly
OL,9,Fresignation and said the process
OL,10,Fshould be completed by September.
OL,12,FAssuming a leadership contest is
OL,13,Ftriggered in late June or early July,
OL,14,Fthen late August or early September
OL,15,Fwould be the most likely date for the
OL,16,Fend of the race.
